2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:25,661
ظآزBecause you existظآز

3
00:00:25,662 --> 00:00:27,741
ظآزYou're alwaysظآز

4
00:00:27,742 --> 00:00:32,391
ظآزSomewhere close, flying with meظآز

5
00:00:32,392 --> 00:00:35,124
ظآزGo to where the wind blowsظآز

6
00:00:35,125 --> 00:00:36,691
ظآزHold tightظآز

7
00:00:36,692 --> 00:00:42,481
ظآزTo the ray of light that belongs to usظآز

8
00:00:42,482 --> 00:00:48,170
=Wild & Fiery=
=Episode 22=

9
00:00:49,059 --> 00:00:51,100
Mr. He, what brings you here today?

10
00:00:52,100 --> 00:00:53,739
I heard that you
are very capable, Miss Yan,

11
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,180
so I wanted to meet you.

12
00:00:57,019 --> 00:00:58,459
Is Mr. Hong

13
00:00:58,460 --> 00:00:59,299
not here today?

14
00:01:00,460 --> 00:01:02,060
I'm sorry, Mr. He.

15
00:01:02,259 --> 00:01:03,618
Mr. Hong has been away lately,

16
00:01:03,619 --> 00:01:04,980
and he doesn't see people easily.

17
00:01:06,499 --> 00:01:07,659
Then, it's really

18
00:01:07,779 --> 00:01:09,140
unfortunate today.

19
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:11,340
What a pity.

20
00:01:11,540 --> 00:01:12,858
I originally had a collaboration

21
00:01:12,859 --> 00:01:15,099
I wanted to discuss with Mr. Hong.

22
00:01:15,419 --> 00:01:16,618
What collaboration?

23
00:01:16,619 --> 00:01:17,819
Why don't you tell me about it?

24
00:01:17,940 --> 00:01:19,420
You are a smart person,

25
00:01:19,619 --> 00:01:21,420
so I'll be blunt.

26
00:01:21,460 --> 00:01:22,819
He Group

27
00:01:22,820 --> 00:01:24,379
wants to cooperate with Mr. Hong

28
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:26,819
to auction his new work,
"Changing Mountains and Rivers."

29
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:35,819
Why are you here?

30
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:39,739
Boss,

31
00:01:40,020 --> 00:01:41,459
your rival is causing trouble again.

32
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:42,620
What is he up to now?

33
00:01:44,419 --> 00:01:45,579
He's looking for Hong

34
00:01:45,580 --> 00:01:46,739
to deal with you.

35
00:01:53,499 --> 00:01:54,900
Why are you here?

36
00:01:56,139 --> 00:01:56,819
Miss Mu,

37
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,858
don't get the wrong idea.

38
00:01:57,859 --> 00:01:59,539
I'm here for business.

39
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:02,258
Don't be so nervous.

40
00:02:02,259 --> 00:02:04,819
I was just curious
and dropped by to take a look.

41
00:02:05,979 --> 00:02:08,460
If you want to talk business later,
you can just go to the office.

42
00:02:08,779 --> 00:02:11,299
I came here today
to give you an important piece of news.

43
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:12,539
I don't want others to know.

44
00:02:12,779 --> 00:02:13,900
What news?

45
00:02:14,379 --> 00:02:15,378
He Min

46
00:02:15,379 --> 00:02:17,900
wants to secure Mr. Hong's new work,
"Changing Mountains and Rivers."

47
00:02:17,939 --> 00:02:18,739
He plans to use it

48
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:21,139
to outshine the Mu Group at the auction.

49
00:02:23,099 --> 00:02:24,378
The message is delivered.

50
00:02:24,379 --> 00:02:25,259
I'm leaving now.

51
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,338
Don't worry.

52
00:02:29,339 --> 00:02:30,659
He Min won't succeed.

53
00:02:31,420 --> 00:02:32,538
But last time, our Mu Group

54
00:02:32,539 --> 00:02:34,379
completely offended Mr. Hong.

55
00:02:36,460 --> 00:02:38,099
I'm afraid he really will choose He Min.

56
00:02:40,779 --> 00:02:42,979
Miss Yan has already come to warn us.

57
00:02:42,980 --> 00:02:44,659
Maybe there's still a chance.

58
00:03:34,339 --> 00:03:35,180
Try this.

59
00:03:48,900 --> 00:03:51,098
To our first official date,

60
00:03:51,099 --> 00:03:51,859
cheers.

61
00:04:00,939 --> 00:04:02,419
Since it's our first date,

62
00:04:02,499 --> 00:04:03,900
