63
00:04:05,499 --> 00:04:07,580
You guessed what I was thinking again?

64
00:04:09,339 --> 00:04:11,460
Then, guess what I'm thinking?

65
00:04:14,819 --> 00:04:16,020
Could it be

66
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,780
that you have other arrangements?

67
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:39,260
Now, leave yourself to me.

68
00:04:39,299 --> 00:04:40,539
I'll be your eyes.

69
00:04:41,820 --> 00:04:43,900
Is this another way
for you to decompress?

70
00:04:46,539 --> 00:04:47,979
Wait and see.

71
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:55,619
You're very different today.
Where did you learn this?

72
00:05:18,962 --> 00:05:21,978
ظآزBefore boarding the planeظآز

73
00:05:21,979 --> 00:05:22,739
