76
00:05:33,962 --> 00:05:39,549
ظآزThe luggage in handظآز

77
00:05:39,550 --> 00:05:44,232
ظآزIs both strange and familiarظآز

78
00:05:49,425 --> 00:05:56,011
ظآزWe once made a promiseظآز

79
00:05:56,012 --> 00:06:02,424
ظآزTo leave our footprints
all over the worldظآز

80
00:06:02,425 --> 00:06:06,349
ظآزBut unfortunately, nowظآز

81
00:06:06,350 --> 00:06:10,632
ظآزYou broke that promiseظآز

82
00:06:11,962 --> 00:06:18,532
ظآزThe world you want to chaseظآز

83
00:06:21,099 --> 00:06:23,020
You prepared all this for me?

84
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:25,979
Do you like it?

85
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,780
I designed these for you myself.

86
00:06:31,100 --> 00:06:34,682
ظآزWatching you goظآز

87
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:35,900
So,

88
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:40,059
